hange.com/questions/2527/why-dont-teeth-glow","last_activity_date":1380115586,"creation_date":1339050149,"answer_count":2,"title":"Why don't teeth glow?","body":"<p>Hydroxyapatite is the main component of tooth enamel. It contains phosphorus in the form of phosphates, pyrophosphates etc. that are found to exhibit the the property of phosphorescence. But why don't the teeth glow in the dark ?<\/p>\n","question_id":2527,"tags":["human-biology","teeth"],"score":34,"accepted_answer_id":2538,"down_vote_count":1,"is_answered":true,"view_count":971,"up_vote_count":35,"last_edit_date":1339083815},{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/4277666449f41474561f867f04f32b73?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG","user_type":"registered","user_id":158,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/158/harpalss","reputation":1335,"display_name":"harpalss","accept_rate":74},"answers":[{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/455979252afd4b28ccbdefdf7d99c5aa?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG","user_type":"registered","user_id":3887,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/3887/jwillis0720","reputation":497,"display_name":"jwillis0720","accept_rate":100},"score":1,"is_accepted":false,"down_vote_count":0,"last_activity_date":1372326188,"creation_date":1372326188,"body":"<p>Try this out with BioPython:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>from Bio.PDB.PDBSuperimposer import PDBSuperimposer as superimposer\nfrom Bio.PDB.PDBParser import PDBParser\n\nparser = PDBParser()\nsup = superimposer()\nstruct_1 = parser.get_structure(\"XXXX\",\"first_pdb\")\nstruct_2 = parser.get_structure(\"XXXX\",\"second_pdb\")\n\natoms1 = struct_1.get_atoms()\natoms2 = struct_2.get_atoms()\nsup.set_atoms(atoms1,atoms2)\n\nprint sup.rotrans #print the rotation translation matrix from the SVD\n\n#then to complete the alignment\nsup.apply()  \n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>You can look here for further details. <a href=\"http://biopython.org/DIST/docs/api/Bio.PDB.Superimposer%27-pysrc.html#Superimposer\" rel=\"nofollow\">