 of cell division, in a typical cell line, and where I might find information on this? Thanks!<\/p>\n","question_id":10533,"tags":["cell-biology","cellular-respiration"],"score":2,"down_vote_count":0,"is_answered":false,"view_count":74,"up_vote_count":2,"last_edit_date":1379869839}]}